&lt;p&gt;Good Inside is seeking a Machine Learning Engineer to join our Engineering team. This is &lt;strong&gt;not&lt;/strong&gt; a research or data science role – we’re looking for a strong backend engineer who has hands-on experience shipping ML-powered features in production. You’ll work at the intersection of backend systems and machine learning, building the infrastructure and services that bring personalized, intelligent experiences to our users.&lt;/p&gt;
